{"type":"message","id":"da166605","parentId":"7c1215c1","timestamp":"2026-03-21T01:33:36.847Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"看到trading_monitor.log还在，这个是交易监控的日志，不是edict的，所以保留。现在总结一下清理结果。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 💼 **Edict项目清理完成**\n\n## ✅ 已清理内容\n\n**进程和服务：**\n1. ✅ 停止并删除 pm2 edict-dashboard 服务\n2. ✅ 停止监控守护进程（PID 970）\n3. ✅ 停止 7891 服务进程（PID 1041）\n\n**数据清理：**\n4. ✅ 清空 agents 目录下所有 agent 配置（11个）\n5. ✅ 清空 data 目录下所有配置文件\n   - agent_config.json\n   - live_status.json\n   - tasks_source.json\n   - pending_model_changes.json\n   - model_change_log.json\n   - sync_status.json\n   - 所有锁文件\n\n**脚本清理：**\n6. ✅ 删除启动脚本（4个）\n   - deploy_edict.sh\n   - start_monitor_7891.sh\n   - start_dashboard.sh\n   - start_edict.sh\n   - ensure_pm2_services.sh\n   - monitor_7891_daemon.sh\n\n**日志清理：**\n7. ✅ 删除监控和 pm2 日志文件\n\n**配置更新：**\n8. ✅ 更新 HEARTBEAT.md（移除 Edict 服务检查项）\n9. ✅ 更新 IDENTITY.md（移除三省六部系统描述）\n\n## 📁 保留内容\n\n- `projects/edict/` 目录（项目源码，可随时重新部署）\n- `data/schema.json`（数据结构定义）\n- `agents/` 目录结构（11个空目录）\n\n---\n\n**验证结果：**\n- ✅ 无 edict 相关进程\n- ✅ pm2 无管理服务\n- ✅ 7891 端口已释放\n\n老板，edict项目已完全清理干净，随时可以重新部署。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":579,"output":421,"cacheRead":36992,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":37992,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774056803691}}
