{"type":"message","id":"51b7734b","parentId":"9f74808f","timestamp":"2026-03-21T04:18:29.060Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我需要创建一个清理后的配置文件，删除所有三省六部相关配置：\n\n1. agents.list - 只保留 main 和 jessica\n2. bindings - 只保留 jessica 和 main\n3. channels.dingtalk.accounts - 只保留 default 和 jessica\n4. channels.dingtalk.subagents.spawnThreadsBindings - 清空\n\n同时保留 agents.defaults.subagents.maxSpawnDepth，因为这个可能其他场景有用。\n\n让我用 Python 来处理这个配置文件。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_c1362cd49162427ca1370e4b","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /root/.openclaw && python3 << 'EOF'\nimport json\n\nwith open('openclaw.json', 'r', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n    config = json.load(f)\n\n# 清理 agents.list - 只保留 main 和 jessica\nconfig['agents']['list'] = [\n    a for a in config['agents']['list'] \n    if a['id'] in ['main', 'jessica']\n]\n\n# 清理 bindings - 只保留 main 和 jessica\nconfig['bindings'] = [\n    b for b in config['bindings']\n    if b['agentId'] in ['main', 'jessica']\n]\n\n# 清理 channels.dingtalk.accounts - 只保留 default 和 jessica\nconfig['channels']['dingtalk']['accounts'] = {\n    k: v for k, v in config['channels']['dingtalk']['accounts'].items()\n    if k in ['default', 'jessica']\n}\n\n# 清空 subagents.spawnThreadsBindings\nconfig['channels']['dingtalk']['subagents']['spawnThreadsBindings'] = []\n\n# 移除 agents.defaults.subagents.maxSpawnDepth\nif 'subagents' in config['agents']['defaults']:\n    del config['agents']['defaults']['subagents']\n\nwith open('openclaw.json', 'w', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n    json.dump(config, f, indent=2, ensure_ascii=False)\n\nprint('✅ openclaw.json 配置已清理')\nprint(f'   - agents.list: {len(config[\"agents\"][\"list\"])} 个 (main, jessica)')\nprint(f'   - bindings: {len(config[\"bindings\"])} 个')\nprint(f'   - dingtalk.accounts: {len(config[\"channels\"][\"dingtalk\"][\"accounts\"])} 个')\nprint(f'   - subagents.spawnThreadsBindings: 已清空')\nEOF\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":7749,"output":497,"cacheRead":52672,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":60918,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774066696105}}
