{"type":"message","id":"f318de45","parentId":"8095a00e","timestamp":"2026-03-21T04:22:02.989Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"文档已创建成功。现在让我验证文件并告诉用户。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] ✅ **配置文档已生成**\n\n**保存位置：** `/root/.openclaw/workspace/Knowledge/openclaw-config-reference.md`\n\n**文档内容（15KB）：**\n\n| 章节 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| 1. meta | 元数据信息 |\n| 2. wizard | 向导配置 |\n| 3. browser | 浏览器配置 |\n| 4. models | 模型配置（含 16 个模型详情） |\n| 5. agents | Agent 配置（defaults + list） |\n| 6. tools | 工具配置 |\n| 7. bindings | 绑定配置 |\n| 8. commands | 命令配置 |\n| 9. session | 会话配置 |\n| 10. hooks | 钩子配置 |\n| 11. channels | 通道配置（钉钉账号详情） |\n| 12. gateway | 网关配置 |\n| 13. plugins | 插件配置（EverMemOS 详情） |\n\n**包含：**\n- 所有配置项的字段说明\n- 当前配置的实际值示例\n- 常见配置场景（添加 Agent、账号、模型）\n- 修改注意事项"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":5911,"output":272,"cacheRead":67008,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":73191,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774066913013}}
