{"type":"message","id":"5d30224f","parentId":"a0941a5a","timestamp":"2026-03-21T04:27:35.415Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"文档已成功创建。让我给用户一个总结。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] ✅ **Agents 目录配置文档已生成**\n\n**保存位置：** `/root/.openclaw/knowledge-base/openclaw-agents-directory-reference.md`\n\n**文档内容（10.7KB）：**\n\n| 章节 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| 1. 目录结构概览 | agents 目录整体结构 |\n| 2. Agent 目录结构 | 每个 agent 的子目录说明 |\n| 3. SOUL.md | 身份配置文件格式和示例 |\n| 4. agent 目录 | config.yaml、models.json、auth-profiles.json 详解 |\n| 5. sessions 目录 | 会话索引和历史文件格式 |\n| 6. 当前 Agents | 活跃和已清理的 agent 列表 |\n| 7. 最佳实践 | 创建新 agent 和优化建议 |\n\n**知识库当前内容：**\n```\n.openclaw/knowledge-base/\n├── openclaw-config-reference.md          (18KB - 主配置参考)\n├── openclaw-agents-directory-reference.md (11KB - Agents目录参考)\n└── 金蝶云苍穹/                           (金蝶相关文档)\n```"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":274,"output":253,"cacheRead":91968,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":92495,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774067246399}}
