{"type":"message","id":"4ff2efab","parentId":"5b957cce","timestamp":"2026-03-21T04:35:14.420Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"很好！GitHub 访问正常，返回 HTTP 200。现在让我生成一个总结。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] ✅ **GitHub520 hosts 更新完成**\n\n**执行步骤：**\n1. ✅ 备份 hosts 文件 → `/etc/hosts.backup.20260321_123447`\n2. ✅ 获取 GitHub520 最新 hosts（更新时间：2026-03-21 10:59:47）\n3. ✅ 追加到 `/etc/hosts` 文件\n4. ✅ 验证 GitHub 访问正常（HTTP 200）\n\n**添加的域名（部分）：**\n- github.com → 140.82.113.3\n- api.github.com → 20.205.243.168\n- raw.githubusercontent.com → 185.199.110.133\n- codeload.github.com → 20.205.243.165\n- github.global.ssl.fastly.net → 151.101.193.194\n- ... 以及其他 40+ GitHub 相关域名\n\n**说明：**\n- hosts 文件会自动生效，无需重启 DNS 服务\n- 建议每月更新一次以保持最佳访问速度\n- 如需还原：`cp /etc/hosts.backup.20260321_123447 /etc/hosts`"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":332,"output":281,"cacheRead":101888,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":102501,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774067703311}}
