{"type":"message","id":"4123fd54","parentId":"9fcefcd4","timestamp":"2026-03-21T05:55:50.512Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"问题很明显了，@vitejs/plugin-react确实没有安装。让我用yarn试试，或者直接从npm registry下载这个包。\n\n其实最简单的方法是：直接使用--legacy-peer-deps或者--force，并且指定具体的版本号。让我试试用npm直接安装到node_modules目录。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_0c45363ac2274b34b599d009","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /root/clawd/gui/node_modules && npm install @vitejs/plugin-react@5 @types/react-dom@19 --no-save 2>&1 | tail -10","timeout":60}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":383,"output":116,"cacheRead":57088,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":57587,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774072544382}}
{"type":"message","id":"9a8c773b","parentId":"4123fd54","timestamp":"2026-03-21T05:55:52.711Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_0c45363ac2274b34b599d009","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"up to date, audited 82 packages in 2s\n\n11 packages are looking for funding\n  run `npm fund` for details\n\nfound 0 vulnerabilities"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":2124,"aggregated":"up to date, audited 82 packages in 2s\n\n11 packages are looking for funding\n  run `npm fund` for details\n\nfound 0 vulnerabilities","cwd":"/root/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774072552655}}
{"type":"message","id":"db3dabc9","parentId":"9a8c773b","timestamp":"2026-03-21T05:56:05.361Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"npm说\"up to date\"但实际文件不在。这可能是npm缓存问题。让我尝试：\n1. 清除npm缓存\n2. 或者直接从registry下载tarball并解压\n\n或者，我可以直接放弃这个有问题的项目，使用另一个更简单的方案：直接恢复之前的openclaw.json配置，不使用这个三省六部系统。\n\n让我先问问用户想怎么办。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 💼 老板，遇到 npm 依赖问题了。\n\n## 当前状态\n\n**已完成：**\n- ✅ 三省六部工作区已创建：`~/clawd/`\n- ✅ Dashboard GUI 已下载：`~/clawd/gui/`\n- ✅ 配置文件已生成并简化为 WebUI 模式\n- ✅ 只保留 silijian agent\n\n**卡在：**\n- ❌ 前端构建失败\n- ❌ `@vitejs/plugin-react` 和 `@types/react-dom` 无法正确安装\n- ❌ npm 显示 \"up to date\" 但实际文件不存在\n\n## 解决方案\n\n**方案 A：跳过前端，直接用后端**\n```bash\ncd ~/clawd/gui/server\nBOLUO_AUTH_TOKEN=123456 node index.js\n```\n访问：`http://你的IP:18795`\n\n**方案 B：恢复旧配置**\n刚才备份了你的旧配置，可以恢复：\n```bash\ncp /root/.openclaw/openclaw.json.old /root/.openclaw/openclaw.json\n```\n\n**方案 C：重新下载整个项目**\n从 GitHub 下载 release 版本，可能有预构建文件。\n\n---\n\n你想用哪个方案？还是直接放弃这个三省六部项目？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":217,"output":361,"cacheRead":57408,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":57986,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774072552714}}
