{"type":"message","id":"fa95f03e","parentId":"134119ec","timestamp":"2026-03-21T06:02:56.627Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我看到钉钉配置了。现在需要：\n1. 添加太子（司礼监）agent\n2. 添加对应的钉钉账号（需要用户提供钉钉机器人配置）\n3. 配置 bindings\n\n但用户没有提供太子的钉钉机器人配置，我需要先问用户要这些信息。\n\n不过，用户说\"帮我把太子的钉钉配置\"，可能是想让我配置太子agent使用现有的钉钉账号？让我先创建太子agent的配置，然后询问钉钉账号信息。\n\n或者，用户可能想让我把太子配置成使用钉钉通道。让我先创建太子agent配置，使用现有的default钉钉账号。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_4375468955984d8cab731337","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 << 'EOF'\nimport json\n\nwith open('/root/.openclaw/openclaw.json', 'r') as f:\n    config = json.load(f)\n\n# 创建太子（司礼监）agent\ntaizi_agent = {\n    \"id\": \"taizi\",\n    \"name\": \"司礼监\",\n    \"workspace\": \"/root/clawd\",\n    \"model\": \"zai/glm-5\",\n    \"agentDir\": \"/root/.openclaw/agents/taizi/agent\",\n    \"identity\": {\n        \"name\": \"司礼监\",\n        \"theme\": \"\"\"你是菠萝王朝的司礼监，负责日常对话和任务调度。\n\n## 铁律\n1. 废话不要多 — 说重点\n2. 汇报要及时 — 做完就说\n3. 做事要靠谱 — 先想后做\n\n## 沟通风格\n- 中文为主\n- 直接说结论，需要细节再展开\n\n## 朝廷架构\n- 司礼监：日常调度、任务分配\n- 内阁：战略决策、方案审议、全局规划\n- 都察院：监察审计、代码审查、质量把控\n- 兵部：软件工程、系统架构\n- 户部：财务预算、电商运营\n- 礼部：品牌营销、内容创作\n- 工部：DevOps、服务器运维\n- 吏部：项目管理、创业孵化\n- 刑部：法务合规、知识产权\n- 翰林院：学术研究、知识整理、文档撰写\n- 国子监：教育培训、知识管理、学习规划\n- 太医院：健康管理、饮食营养、训练计划\n- 内务府：日常起居、日程安排、后勤保障\n- 御膳房：膳食安排、美食推荐、食谱研究\n\n## 工作方式\n- 接收皇上下达的旨意\n- 简单任务直接回复\n- 复杂任务使用 sessions_spawn 派发给对应部门\n- 完成后及时汇报结果\"\"\"\n    }\n}\n\n# 添加到 agents.list\nif 'agents' not in config:\n    config['agents'] = {}\nif 'list' not in config['agents']:\n    config['agents']['list'] = []\n\n# 检查是否已存在\nexisting_ids = [a['id'] for a in config['agents']['list']]\nif 'taizi' not in existing_ids:\n    config['agents']['list'].append(taizi_agent)\n    print(\"✅ 已添加太子 agent\")\nelse:\n    print(\"⚠️ 太子 agent 已存在\")\n\n# 添加钉钉账号配置（使用 default 账号）\n# 注意：这里需要用户提供新的钉钉机器人配置\n# 暂时让太子使用 default 账号\n\n# 更新 bindings\nif 'bindings' not in config:\n    config['bindings'] = []\n\n# 检查是否已有太子 binding\ntaizi_binding_exists = any(b.get('agentId') == 'taizi' for b in config['bindings'])\nif not taizi_binding_exists:\n    config['bindings'].append({\n        \"agentId\": \"taizi\",\n        \"match\": {\n            \"channel\": \"dingtalk\",\n            \"accountId\": \"default\"\n        }\n    })\n    print(\"✅ 已添加太子 binding\")\n\n# 保存\nwith open('/root/.openclaw/openclaw.json', 'w') as f:\n    json.dump(config, f, indent=2, ensure_ascii=False)\n\nprint(\"\\n当前 agents:\")\nfor a in config['agents']['list']:\n    print(f\"  - {a['id']}: {a.get('name', 'N/A')}\")\n\nprint(\"\\n当前 bindings:\")\nfor b in config['bindings']:\n    print(f\"  - {b.get('agentId')}: {b.get('match', {})}\")\nEOF\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":785,"output":963,"cacheRead":67200,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":68948,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774072949176}}
{"type":"message","id":"eded9c39","parentId":"fa95f03e","timestamp":"2026-03-21T06:02:56.766Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_4375468955984d8cab731337","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"✅ 已添加太子 agent\n✅ 已添加太子 binding\n\n当前 agents:\n  - main: 日常助手\n  - jessica: jessica\n  - taizi: 司礼监\n\n当前 bindings:\n  - jessica: {'channel': 'dingtalk', 'accountId': 'jessica'}\n  - main: {'channel': 'dingtalk', 'accountId': 'default'}\n  - taizi: {'channel': 'dingtalk', 'accountId': 'default'}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":107,"aggregated":"✅ 已添加太子 agent\n✅ 已添加太子 binding\n\n当前 agents:\n  - main: 日常助手\n  - jessica: jessica\n  - taizi: 司礼监\n\n当前 bindings:\n  - jessica: {'channel': 'dingtalk', 'accountId': 'jessica'}\n  - main: {'channel': 'dingtalk', 'accountId': 'default'}\n  - taizi: {'channel': 'dingtalk', 'accountId': 'default'}","cwd":"/root/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774072976757}}
