{"type":"message","id":"66524c25","parentId":"2b0c897a","timestamp":"2026-03-21T06:03:23.218Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我需要重启Gateway让配置生效。但是有个问题：太子和main都绑定了default账号，这会导致冲突。\n\n让我先检查一下当前的配置，然后重启Gateway，看看会发生什么。或者我应该先提醒用户这个问题。\n\n实际上，bindings的匹配规则是：第一个匹配的agent会处理消息。所以如果main在前面，main会处理；如果taizi在前面，taizi会处理。\n\n让我检查bindings的顺序。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_94573966c3d4463693a96c94","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 << 'EOF'\nimport json\n\nwith open('/root/.openclaw/openclaw.json', 'r') as f:\n    config = json.load(f)\n\nprint(\"当前 bindings 顺序：\")\nfor i, b in enumerate(config['bindings']):\n    print(f\"  {i+1}. {b.get('agentId')}: {b.get('match', {})}\")\n\nprint(\"\\n⚠️ 注意：main 和 taizi 都绑定了 default 账号\")\nprint(\"   这会导致消息路由冲突！\")\nprint(\"\\n建议方案：\")\nprint(\"  A. 给太子创建新的钉钉机器人\")\nprint(\"  B. 太子接管 default，main 改用别的\")\nprint(\"  C. 使用不同的匹配规则区分\")\nEOF\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":598,"output":259,"cacheRead":68992,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":69849,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774072993602}}
{"type":"message","id":"f17ffa50","parentId":"66524c25","timestamp":"2026-03-21T06:03:23.318Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_94573966c3d4463693a96c94","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"当前 bindings 顺序：\n  1. jessica: {'channel': 'dingtalk', 'accountId': 'jessica'}\n  2. main: {'channel': 'dingtalk', 'accountId': 'default'}\n  3. taizi: {'channel': 'dingtalk', 'accountId': 'default'}\n\n⚠️ 注意：main 和 taizi 都绑定了 default 账号\n   这会导致消息路由冲突！\n\n建议方案：\n  A. 给太子创建新的钉钉机器人\n  B. 太子接管 default，main 改用别的\n  C. 使用不同的匹配规则区分"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":39,"aggregated":"当前 bindings 顺序：\n  1. jessica: {'channel': 'dingtalk', 'accountId': 'jessica'}\n  2. main: {'channel': 'dingtalk', 'accountId': 'default'}\n  3. taizi: {'channel': 'dingtalk', 'accountId': 'default'}\n\n⚠️ 注意：main 和 taizi 都绑定了 default 账号\n   这会导致消息路由冲突！\n\n建议方案：\n  A. 给太子创建新的钉钉机器人\n  B. 太子接管 default，main 改用别的\n  C. 使用不同的匹配规则区分","cwd":"/root/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774073003310}}
{"type":"message","id":"cdade6b0","parentId":"f17ffa50","timestamp":"2026-03-21T06:03:39.395Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我需要向用户说明这个情况，并提供解决方案。用户需要决定：\n1. 是否创建新的钉钉机器人给太子\n2. 还是要太子接管现有的机器人\n\n让我先问用户想怎么处理。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] ⚠️ **配置有问题！**\n\n## 当前状态\n\n已添加太子 agent，但发现**冲突**：\n\n```\nbindings:\n1. jessica → dingtalk:jessica\n2. main    → dingtalk:default  ← 冲突\n3. taizi   → dingtalk:default  ← 冲突\n```\n\n**问题：** `main` 和 `taizi` 都绑定了同一个钉钉机器人（default），消息会乱。\n\n---\n\n## 解决方案\n\n**方案 A：太子用新机器人（推荐）**\n- 在钉钉开放平台创建新机器人\n- 我帮你配置到 openclaw.json\n- 太子有独立的钉钉入口\n\n**方案 B：太子接管 default**\n- 太子用 default 机器人\n- main 改名或禁用\n\n**方案 C：按聊天类型区分**\n- 私聊 → main\n- 群聊 → taizi\n\n---\n\n**你需要提供：**\n- 如果选 A：新的钉钉机器人 clientId、clientSecret、agentId\n- 如果选 B/C：直接告诉我\n\n你的钉钉机器人配置在哪里？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":412,"output":284,"cacheRead":69568,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":70264,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774073003321}}
