{"type":"message","id":"e39f82e1","parentId":"0130ce6b","timestamp":"2026-03-21T06:04:11.427Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"密码已经改好了。现在需要处理太子的钉钉配置。\n\n用户说\"帮我把太子的钉钉配置\"，但没有提供新的钉钉机器人信息。\n\n让我先检查一下当前的配置情况，然后问用户：\n1. 是否要给太子创建新的钉钉机器人？\n2. 还是太子用现有的某个账号？\n\n不过，根据之前的经验，用户可能希望太子有自己的钉钉机器人。让我直接问用户要配置信息。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_e1cd097d7459412c9e4a556f","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 << 'EOF'\nimport json\n\nwith open('/root/.openclaw/openclaw.json', 'r') as f:\n    config = json.load(f)\n\n# 显示当前钉钉账号\naccounts = config.get('channels', {}).get('dingtalk', {}).get('accounts', {})\nprint(\"当前钉钉账号：\")\nfor acc_id, acc in accounts.items():\n    print(f\"  {acc_id}:\")\n    print(f\"    - clientId: {acc.get('clientId', 'N/A')}\")\n    print(f\"    - agentId: {acc.get('agentId', 'N/A')}\")\n    print(f\"    - corpId: {acc.get('corpId', 'N/A')}\")\n\nprint(\"\\n当前 bindings：\")\nfor b in config.get('bindings', []):\n    print(f\"  {b.get('agentId')} → {b.get('match', {})}\")\n\nprint(\"\\n⚠️ 问题：main 和 taizi 都绑定到 default 账号\")\nprint(\"   需要给太子创建新的钉钉机器人或重新分配\")\nEOF\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":412,"output":327,"cacheRead":71296,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":72035,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774073041726}}
{"type":"message","id":"7d9b7e9b","parentId":"e39f82e1","timestamp":"2026-03-21T06:04:11.599Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_e1cd097d7459412c9e4a556f","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"当前钉钉账号：\n  default:\n    - clientId: ding46pdp4gp2nfgfbfl\n    - agentId: 4271180067\n    - corpId: ding3cecc6cee84e6509a1320dcb25e91351\n  jessica:\n    - clientId: dingftzhsams5mrc5qk0\n    - agentId: 4274267137\n    - corpId: ding3cecc6cee84e6509a1320dcb25e91351\n\n当前 bindings：\n  jessica → {'channel': 'dingtalk', 'accountId': 'jessica'}\n  main → {'channel': 'dingtalk', 'accountId': 'default'}\n  taizi → {'channel': 'dingtalk', 'accountId': 'default'}\n\n⚠️ 问题：main 和 taizi 都绑定到 default 账号\n   需要给太子创建新的钉钉机器人或重新分配"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":124,"aggregated":"当前钉钉账号：\n  default:\n    - clientId: ding46pdp4gp2nfgfbfl\n    - agentId: 4271180067\n    - corpId: ding3cecc6cee84e6509a1320dcb25e91351\n  jessica:\n    - clientId: dingftzhsams5mrc5qk0\n    - agentId: 4274267137\n    - corpId: ding3cecc6cee84e6509a1320dcb25e91351\n\n当前 bindings：\n  jessica → {'channel': 'dingtalk', 'accountId': 'jessica'}\n  main → {'channel': 'dingtalk', 'accountId': 'default'}\n  taizi → {'channel': 'dingtalk', 'accountId': 'default'}\n\n⚠️ 问题：main 和 taizi 都绑定到 default 账号\n   需要给太子创建新的钉钉机器人或重新分配","cwd":"/root/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774073051577}}
{"type":"message","id":"540a263b","parentId":"7d9b7e9b","timestamp":"2026-03-21T06:04:23.831Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在有两个选择：\n1. 让用户创建新的钉钉机器人给太子\n2. 让太子和 main 共用一个机器人，但通过其他方式区分（比如群聊 vs 私聊）\n\n我应该先问用户要新的钉钉配置，还是提供其他解决方案。\n\n根据用户之前的反馈，他可能不想太麻烦。让我提供一个简单的方案：\n- 太子用群聊模式\n- main 用私聊模式\n\n或者，我可以让太子接管 default，main 改用其他名字。\n\n不过，最简单的方式是：让太子使用 default 账号，main 改名或禁用。\n\n让我问用户。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] ✅ **密码已修改**\n\n**Dashboard 登录密码：** `xiaoyang0`  \n**访问地址：** `http://你的IP:18795`\n\n---\n\n## ⚠️ 钉钉配置冲突\n\n**当前状态：**\n```\njessica → dingtalk:jessica  ✅\nmain    → dingtalk:default  ⚠️ 冲突\ntaizi   → dingtalk:default  ⚠️ 冲突\n```\n\n**问题：** `main` 和 `taizi` 绑定了同一个钉钉机器人，消息会乱。\n\n---\n\n## 解决方案\n\n**方案 1：太子用新机器人（推荐）**\n- 在钉钉开放平台创建新机器人\n- 提供 clientId、clientSecret、agentId\n- 我帮你配置\n\n**方案 2：太子接管 default**\n- 太子用 default 机器人\n- main 禁用或改名\n\n**方案 3：按聊天类型区分**\n- 私聊 → main\n- 群聊 → taizi\n\n---\n\n**你想用哪个方案？** 如果选方案1，请提供新机器人的配置信息。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":572,"output":379,"cacheRead":71680,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":72631,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774073051604}}
