{"type":"message","id":"c8842b90","parentId":"7f1277cf","timestamp":"2026-03-21T06:13:02.260Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"完美！所有服务都在正常运行：\n1. PM2 管理 Dashboard 服务（boluo-gui-server）- 状态 online\n2. Gateway 正常运行（18789端口）- 状态 live\n3. Dashboard 页面正常加载 - 显示\"菠萝王朝管理后台\"\n\n现在让我更新一下记忆文件，记录今天的成果","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_e3fc234dca514526b7c74da6","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-03-21.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":505,"output":92,"cacheRead":85248,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":85845,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774073576005}}
{"type":"message","id":"5177053f","parentId":"c8842b90","timestamp":"2026-03-21T06:13:02.338Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_e3fc234dca514526b7c74da6","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 2026-03-21 记忆\n\n## Edict三省六部项目清理\n\n**时间：** 08:14-12:27\n\n### 清理内容\n1. **停止服务**\n   - pm2 edict-dashboard 服务\n   - 7891端口监控守护进程\n   - 监控启动脚本\n\n2. **删除目录**\n   - `projects/edict/` 项目目录\n   - `projects/edict.zip` 备份文件\n   - `projects/edict_backup_20260320_081322/` 备份目录\n   - 11个三省六部agents目录（taizi, zhongshu, menxia, shangshu, hubu, libu, bingbu, xingbu, gongbu, libu_hr, zaochao）\n   - 11个workspace目录\n\n3. **清理配置**\n   - 从openclaw.json移除所有三省六部agents配置\n   - 移除所有钉钉账号配置（保留default和jessica）\n   - 移除bindings和subagents配置\n   - 更新HEARTBEAT.md，移除Edict服务检查项\n   - 更新IDENTITY.md，移除三省六部系统描述\n\n### 清理原因\n项目架构设计问题，无法实际使用：\n- maxSpawnDepth限制导致调用链无法完整执行\n- 整体架构过于复杂，维护成本高\n\n---\n\n## 知识库建设\n\n**时间：** 12:21-12:31\n\n### 创建文档\n1. **openclaw-config-reference.md** (18KB)\n   - 13个配置章节完整说明\n   - 所有配置项字段说明\n   - 当前配置的实际值示例\n   - 常见配置场景\n\n2. **openclaw-agents-directory-reference.md** (14KB)\n   - Agents目录结构说明\n   - SOUL.md身份配置格式\n   - agent目录配置文件详解\n   - sessions目录会话数据格式\n   - 配置最佳实践\n\n### 知识库位置\n`~/.openclaw/knowledge-base/`\n```\nknowledge-base/\n├── openclaw/                    # OpenClaw配置文档\n│   ├── openclaw-config-reference.md\n│   └── openclaw-agents-directory-reference.md\n└── 金蝶云苍穹/                  # 金蝶相关文档\n```\n\n### IDENTITY.md更新\n添加了知识库配置章节，说明知识库位置和用途。\n\n---\n\n## GitHub访问优化\n\n**时间：** 12:34\n\n### GitHub520 hosts更新\n- 备份hosts文件到 `/etc/hosts.backup.20260321_123447`\n- 添加40+ GitHub域名IP映射\n- 更新时间：2026-03-21 10:59:47\n- 验证GitHub访问正常（HTTP 200）\n\n### 常用域名\n- github.com → 140.82.113.3\n- api.github.com → 20.205.243.168\n- raw.githubusercontent.com → 185.199.110.133\n- codeload.github.com → 20.205.243.165\n\n---\n\n## 新三省六部安装尝试\n\n**时间：** 13:35-13:53\n\n### 安装内容\n- 项目：wanikua/danghuangshang\n- 安装脚本：install-lite.sh\n- 工作区：~/clawd/\n- 模式：WebUI模式（选项3）\n\n### 遇到问题\n前端构建失败，npm依赖问题：\n- `@types/react-dom` 包未正确安装到node_modules\n- `@vitejs/plugin-react` 包未正确安装\n- 尝试多次清理重装无效\n\n### 已完成配置\n- 配置文件已生成并简化为WebUI模式\n- 只保留silijian agent\n- Dashboard GUI已下载到 ~/clawd/gui/\n\n### 待解决\n需要解决npm依赖问题才能完成前端构建\n\n---\n\n## 当前系统状态\n\n### 运行的服务\n- OpenClaw Gateway（端口18789）\n- 交易系统定时任务（选股8:00-9:00，复盘16:00-17:00）\n\n### 当前配置\n- Agents：main, jessica\n- 钉钉账号：default, jessica\n- 知识库：~/.openclaw/knowledge-base/\n\n### 重要文件位置\n- 主配置：/root/.openclaw/openclaw.json\n- 知识库：~/.openclaw/knowledge-base/\n- 交易策略：/root/.openclaw/workspace/Knowledge/trading-strategies/\n- 日志：/root/.openclaw/workspace/logs/\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774073582329}}
