{"type":"message","id":"0b86fcca","parentId":"457c0a4e","timestamp":"2026-03-21T06:13:44.814Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"完美！所有配置都正确：\n- 3个钉钉账号：default, jessica, taizi（注意这里显示为 'taizi'，可能是用户提供的配置里写的是\"太子\"）\n- 3个 agents：main, jessica, taizi\n- 3个 bindings 都正确映射\n\n现在总结一下完成情况","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] ✅ **PM2 管理配置完成！**\n\n## 📊 系统状态\n\n### PM2 管理服务\n```\n服务名称：boluo-gui-server\n状态：online\n内存：77.8MB\n运行时间：17秒\n开机自启：✅ 已配置\n```\n\n### 服务健康检查\n- ✅ Gateway（18789）：`{\"ok\":true,\"status\":\"live\"}`\n- ✅ Dashboard（18795）：正常访问\n\n### 当前配置\n```\n钉钉账号：\n  - default\n  - jessica  \n  - taizi（太子）\n\nAgents：\n  - main → dingtalk:default\n  - jessica → dingtalk:jessica\n  - taizi → dingtalk:taizi  ✅\n```\n\n---\n\n## 🎯 访问方式\n\n**Dashboard：** `http://你的IP:18795`  \n**密码：** `xiaoyang0`\n\n**钉钉测试：**\n1. 打开钉钉\n2. 找到\"太子\"机器人\n3. 发送消息测试\n\n---\n\n## ✨ 完成项\n\n1. ✅ Dashboard 前端构建（25个文件，700KB）\n2. ✅ Dashboard 后端部署（PM2管理）\n3. ✅ 太子钉钉账号配置\n4. ✅ PM2 开机自启动\n5. ✅ Gateway 健康检查\n6. ✅ 配置持久化\n\n现在系统已完全配置好，PM2 会自动管理 Dashboard 服务！ 🎉"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":282,"output":415,"cacheRead":87744,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":88441,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774073609089}}
