r-- 1 root root  3245 Mar 21 14:23 SOUL.md\ndrwxr-xr-x 1 root root   444 Mar 21 14:23 agents\n-rw-r--r-- 1 root root 22208 Mar 21 14:23 openclaw.json\n\n/root/.openclaw/workspace/projects/danghuangshang/configs/modern-ceo/:\ntotal 16\ndrwxr-xr-x 1 root root    52 Mar 21 14:23 .\ndrwxr-xr-x 1 root root    66 Mar 21 14:23 ..\n-rw-r--r-- 1 root root  3974 Mar 21 14:23 SOUL.md\ndrwxr-xr-x 1 root root   110 Mar 21 14:23 agents\n-rw-r--r-- 1 root root 11003 Mar 21 14:23 openclaw.json\n\n/root/.openclaw/workspace/projects/danghuangshang/configs/tang-sansheng/:\ntotal 20\ndrwxr-xr-x 1 root root    52 Mar 21 14:23 .\ndrwxr-xr-x 1 root root    66 Mar 21 14:23 ..\n-rw-r--r-- 1 root root  3338 Mar 21 14:23 SOUL.md\ndrwxr-xr-x 1 root root   202 Mar 21 14:23 agents\n-rw-r--r-- 1 root root 12987 Mar 21 14:23 openclaw.json","cwd":"/root/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774074301235}}
{"type":"message","id":"623923f6","parentId":"bbfaaa5f","timestamp":"2026-03-21T06:25:19.266Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，有三种制度可选：\n\n1. **ming-neige**（明朝内阁制）- 22KB 配置\n   - 司礼监 + 内阁 + 六部\n   \n2. **modern-ceo**（现代企业制）- 11KB 配置\n   - CEO/CTO/CFO\n   \n3. **tang-sansheng**（唐朝三省制）- 13KB 配置\n   - 中书→门下→尚书\n\n用户提到 `modern-ceo`，但之前我们配置的是\"太子\"（司礼监），这更适合明朝内阁制。\n\n让我询问用户想要哪种制度，然后帮他执行脚本。但是，我需要注意：\n- 这个脚本会覆盖当前的 openclaw.json 配置\n- 我们之前手动配置的 taizi、jessica 等会丢失\n- 需要先备份，然后重新配置钉钉等账号\n\n我应该：\n1. 说明三种制度的区别\n2. 询问用户选择哪种\n3. 备份当前配置\n4. 执行脚本\n5. 重新配置钉钉账号","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 📋 **三种制度可选**\n\n| 制度 | 架构 | 适用场景 | 配置大小 |\n|------|------|----------|---------|\n| **ming-neige** | 司礼监→内阁→六部→都察院 | 个人项目，快速迭代 | 22KB |\n| **modern-ceo** | CEO→Board→CxO | 国际化团队 | 11KB |\n| **tang-sansheng** | 中书省→门下省→尚书省 | 严谨审批流程 | 13KB |\n\n---\n\n## ⚠️ 重要提示\n\n执行脚本会：\n1. ✅ 自动备份当前配置\n2. ❌ **覆盖** openclaw.json（我们手动配置的会丢失）\n3. 需要重新配置钉钉账号\n\n---\n\n## 🎯 你想要哪种？\n\n**推荐：ming-neige（明朝内阁制）**\n- 因为你已经配置了\"太子\"（司礼监）\n- 架构最完整，18个 agents\n- 中文环境友好\n\n**如果选择 ming-neige，流程：**\n1. 备份当前配置\n2. 执行脚本\n3. 重新配置钉钉账号（default, jessica, taizi）\n4. 重启 Gateway\n\n---\n\n告诉我选择：**ming-neige** / **modern-ceo** / **tang-sansheng**？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":736,"output":524,"cacheRead":113408,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":114668,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774074301253}}
