{"type":"message","id":"8f7afab9","parentId":"3cf70569","timestamp":"2026-03-21T06:27:25.071Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，唐朝三省制已经配置好了，有11个agents。但是我发现没有 bindings 配置，需要添加 bindings，并且需要配置 maxSpawnDepth 以支持完整的调用链。\n\n根据之前的经验，调用链是：\n- 中书省（深度0）→ 门下省（深度1）→ 尚书省（深度2）→ 六部（深度3）\n\n所以 maxSpawnDepth 需要设置为至少 4。\n\n让我检查配置并添加必要的设置。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_45a601db4b9f423e986972a1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 << 'EOF'\nimport json\n\nwith open('/root/.openclaw/openclaw.json', 'r') as f:\n    config = json.load(f)\n\n# 检查当前配置\nprint(\"=== 当前配置检查 ===\")\nprint(f\"Agents: {len(config.get('agents', {}).get('list', []))}\")\nprint(f\"Bindings: {len(config.get('bindings', []))}\")\nprint(f\"maxSpawnDepth: {config.get('agents', {}).get('defaults', {}).get('maxSpawnDepth', '未设置')}\")\n\n# 添加 bindings\nif not config.get('bindings'):\n    config['bindings'] = [\n        {\"agentId\": \"zhongshu\", \"match\": {\"channel\": \"dingtalk\", \"accountId\": \"default\"}},\n        {\"agentId\": \"jessica\", \"match\": {\"channel\": \"dingtalk\", \"accountId\": \"jessica\"}},\n        {\"agentId\": \"taizi\", \"match\": {\"channel\": \"dingtalk\", \"accountId\": \"taizi\"}}\n    ]\n    print(\"\\n✅ 已添加 bindings\")\n\n# 设置 maxSpawnDepth\nif 'agents' not in config:\n    config['agents'] = {}\nif 'defaults' not in config['agents']:\n    config['agents']['defaults'] = {}\n\nconfig['agents']['defaults']['maxSpawnDepth'] = 4\nprint(\"✅ 已设置 maxSpawnDepth = 4\")\n\n# 保存\nwith open('/root/.openclaw/openclaw.json', 'w') as f:\n    json.dump(config, f, indent=2, ensure_ascii=False)\n\nprint(\"\\n=== 配置更新完成 ===\")\nprint(f\"Bindings: {len(config['bindings'])}\")\nprint(f\"maxSpawnDepth: {config['agents']['defaults']['maxSpawnDepth']}\")\nEOF\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":1159,"output":484,"cacheRead":117056,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":118699,"cos