higuan         → {'channel': 'discord', 'accountId': 'shiguan'}\n\n=== Agents 配置 ===\n  shangshu        - 尚书省\n  zhongshu        - 中书省\n  menxia          - 门下省\n  yushitai        - 御史台\n  bingbu          - 兵部\n  hubu            - 户部\n  libu            - 礼部\n  gongbu          - 工部\n  libu2           - 吏部\n  xingbu          - 刑部\n  shiguan         - 史官","cwd":"/root/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774074451488}}
{"type":"message","id":"f79ac332","parentId":"61644b4a","timestamp":"2026-03-21T06:27:51.364Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我看到了，配置文件中的 bindings 都是 discord 的，我需要把它们改成 dingtalk。并且要添加我们自己的 agents（main, jessica, taizi）。\n\n让我重新配置 bindings 和 agents。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_f90459f1f2bd406c89499701","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 << 'EOF'\nimport json\n\nwith open('/root/.openclaw/openclaw.json', 'r') as f:\n    config = json.load(f)\n\n# 添加我们的 agents（main, jessica, taizi）到 agents.list\nour_agents = [\n    {\n        \"id\": \"main\",\n        \"default\": True,\n        \"name\": \"日常助手\",\n        \"workspace\": \"/root/.openclaw/workspace\",\n        \"model\": \"zai/glm-5\"\n    },\n    {\n        \"id\": \"jessica\",\n        \"name\": \"jessica\",\n        \"workspace\": \"/root/.openclaw/workspace-jessica\",\n        \"agentDir\": \"/root/.openclaw/agents/jessica/agent\",\n        \"model\": \"zai/glm-4.7\",\n        \"identity\": {\"name\": \"jessica\"}\n    },\n    {\n        \"id\": \"taizi\",\n        \"name\": \"太子\",\n        \"workspace\": \"/root/clawd\",\n        \"agentDir\": \"/root/.openclaw/agents/taizi/agent\",\n        \"model\": \"zai/glm-5\",\n        \"identity\": {\"name\": \"太子\"}\n    }\n]\n\n# 添加到 agents.list\nfor agent in our_agents:\n    if agent['id'] not in [a['id'] for a in config['agents']['list']]:\n        config['agents']['list'].append(agent)\n\n# 更新 bindings - 使用 dingtalk\nconfig['bindings'] = [\n    {\"agentId\": \"main\", \"match\": {\"channel\": \"dingtalk\", \"accountId\": \"default\"}},\n    {\"agentId\": \"jessica\", \"match\": {\"channel\": \"dingtalk\", \"accountId\": \"jessica\"}},\n    {\"agentId\": \"taizi\", \"match\": {\"channel\": \"dingtalk\", \"accountId\": \"taizi\"}},\n    # 唐朝三省的绑定（可选，如果需要钉钉直接访问）\n    {\"agentId\": \"zhongshu\", \"match\": {\"channel\": \"dingtalk\", \"accountId\": \"default\"}},\n    {\"agentId\": \"menxia\", \"match\": {\"channel\": \"dingtalk\", \"accountId\": \"default\"}},\n    {\"agentId\": \"shangshu\", \"match\": {\"channel\": \"dingtalk\", \"accountId\": \"default\"}}\n]\n\n# 保存\nwith open('/root/.openclaw/openclaw.json', 'w') as f:\n    json.dump(config, f, indent=2, ensure_ascii=False)\n\nprint(\"✅ 配置已更新\")\nprint(f\"\\n总 Agents: {len(config['agents']['list'])}\")\nprint(f\"总 Bindings: {len(config['bindings'])}\")\n\nprint(\"\\n=== 所有 Agents ===\")\nfor a in config['agents']['list']:\n    print(f\"  {a['id']:15} - {a.get('name', 'N/A')}\")\n\nprint(\"\\n=== Bindings ===\")\nfor b in config['bindings']:\n    print(f\"  {b['agentId']:15} → {b['match']}\")\nEOF\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":537,"output":705,"cacheRead":118720,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":119962,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774074451500}}
