{"type":"message","id":"ad657302","parentId":"f393de09","timestamp":"2026-03-21T06:34:49.587Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户报告说通过脚本配置后有问题，`openclaw doctor --fix` 报告了多个配置错误：\n\n1. `_regime` - 未识别的键\n2. `agents.list[0].subagents.maxConcurrent` - 未识别的键\n3. `agents.defaults.maxSpawnDepth` - 未识别的键\n4. `models.providers.your-provider.api` - 无效的API选项\n\n用户说脚本配置的JSON在 `.openclaw/knowledge-base/danghuangshang` 目录下，需要手工配置。\n\n从memory中我了解到：\n- 我之前成功识别出maxSpawnDepth=3的限制问题\n- 我精通系统架构限制分析\n- 我具备深度系统分析能力\n\n现在我需要：\n1. 读取原始配置模板\n2. 清理无效配置\n3. 保留有效的agents配置\n4. 修复配置错误\n\n让我先读取配置文件，看看具体问题。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_b3140d2aabfc4460ad934dd5","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 << 'EOF'\nimport json\n\n# 读取当前配置\nwith open('/root/.openclaw/openclaw.json', 'r') as f:\n    config = json.load(f)\n\n# 显示问题配置\nprint(\"=== 需要清理的配置 ===\")\nprint(f\"1. _regime: {config.get('_regime', '不存在')}\")\nprint(f\"2. maxSpawnDepth: {config.get('agents', {}).get('defaults', {}).get('maxSpawnDepth', '不存在')}\")\nprint(f\"3. maxConcurrent: {config.get('agents', {}).get('list', [{}])[0].get('subagents', {}).get('maxConcurrent', '不存在')}\")\nprint(f\"4. your-provider.api: {config.get('models', {}).get('providers', {}).get('your-provider', {}).get('api', '不存在')}\")\n\n# 清理问题配置\nconfig.pop('_regime', None)\nif 'agents' in config and 'defaults' in config['agents']:\n    config['agents']['defaults'].pop('maxSpawnDepth', None)\nif 'agents' in config and 'list' in config['agents'] and config['agents']['list']:\n    for agent in config['agents']['list']:\n        if 'subagents' in agent:\n            agent['subagents'].pop('maxConcurrent', None)\nif 'models' in config and 'providers' in config['models'] and 'your-provider' in config['models']['providers']:\n    config['models']['providers'].pop('your-provider', None)\n\n# 保存\nwith open('/root/.openclaw/openclaw.json', 'w') as f:\n    json.dump(config, f, indent=2, ensure_ascii=False)\n\nprint(\"\\n✅ 已清理问题配置\")\nEOF\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":6918,"output":581,"cacheRead":115712,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":123211,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774074872536}}
