{"type":"message","id":"0c701951","parentId":"9595744d","timestamp":"2026-03-21T06:36:26.656Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Note: Reference memory below. Build on past successes; avoid repeating failed approaches.\n- Time: 2026-03-21 14:36\n\n```text\n<memory>\n  <trait>\n  - [Explicit] [三省六部流程管理] 深度参与并优化三省六部自动流转机制，主动设计测试方案验证subagent自动spawn功能，严格遵循流程管理，发现任务状态标记逻辑错误并立即修复，坚持只有100%完成才算真正完成；优化门下省SOUL.md将核心流程前置，提升流程执行效率；目前使用danghuangshang项目（司礼监→内阁→六部→都察院架构），已配置taizi（司礼监）和Dashboard（端口18795）\n  - [Explicit] [架构优化与问题解决] 精通系统架构限制分析和解决，能够识别maxSpawnDepth等配置问题，提出架构优化方案，具备深度系统分析能力；准确识别出maxSpawnDepth=3导致尚书省无法派发礼部的根本原因，提出修改配置的解决方案\n  - [Explicit] [项目部署与配置] 精通GitHub访问优化和hosts文件管理，能够使用GitHub520等工具解决网络访问问题，实施完整的备份、更新和验证流程；使用开源脚本安装三省六部项目，成功部署boluo-gui-frontend前端项目（构建25个文件，总计约700KB）和Dashboard后端服务（端口18795），配置openclaw agents（main和jessica）\n  - [Explicit] [组织架构与决策] 担任老板职务，负责交易系统整体部署、管理和决策，作为三省六部系统最高决策者，具有完整工作流程掌控能力和最终决策权限\n  - [Explicit] [项目切换与状态管理] 从edict项目切换到danghuangshang项目，当前配置司礼监（taizi）和Dashboard（端口18795），已完成项目克隆；对新项目架构有清晰认知，能快速理解架构差异并做出配置决策\n  </trait>\n  <!-- Relevant skill. Use as reference if applicable to the current task. -->\n  <skill>\n    - name: 交易系统心跳检查流程\n    - description: 当需要验证交易系统所有组件运行状态和定时任务执行情况时使用\n    - content: 最佳实践流程：\n1. 定时任务状态检查\n   - 执行定时任务脚本（如scheduled_tasks.py）\n   - 查看脚本输出最后若干行，确认任务启动状态和监控进程PID\n   - 记录任务执行情况和相关进程ID信息\n   - 确认监控服务是否正常启动并运行\n\n2. 交易监控进程验证\n   - 检查交易监控相关进程（如trading_monitor、trading_hours）\n   - 验证监控进程的实际运行状态\n   - 确认是否有监控进程在后台运行及其具体状态\n   - 记录监控进程的存在和活动情况\n\n3. 告警队列状态检查\n   - 检查告警队列文件（如data/alert_queue.json）\n   - 统计待推送告警的数量，确认队列是否为空\n   - 验证告警处理机制的运行状态\n   - 确保没有积压的告警需要处理\n\n4. 系统资源使用监控\n   - 执行系统命令检查CPU负载（如uptime命令）\n   - 检查内存使用情况（如free命令）\n   - 监控交换分区使用量\n   - 验证系统资源使用是否在正常范围内，确认无资源瓶颈\n\n5. 网关服务健康状态验证\n   - 检查关键服务端口（如本地18789端口）\n   - 验证网关服务的健康状态和响应情况\n   - 确认Gateway服务正常运行且状态为live\n   - 记录服务检查结果和运行状态\n\n6. 心跳状态文件更新\n   - 生成包含所有服务状态的JSON格式数据\n   - 将状态信息保存到指定文件（如memory/heartbeat-state.json）\n   - 记录各组件运行状态、任务完成情况、资源使用数据\n   - 确保状态文件准确反映系统当前状态\n\n7. 系统状态评估与报告\n   - 根据检查结果判断系统整体健康状态\n   - 生成标准化的状态响应（如HEARTBEAT_OK）\n   - 考虑非交易日（如周六）的特殊情况，确认监控已启动待命\n   - 提供详细的系统状态报告供后续参考\n\nPitfalls：\n- 不要只查看定时任务输出而不检查实际进程状态 - 任务声明启动不代表进程实际运行，应验证进程PID和活动状态\n- 避免忽略告警队列的状态检查 - 队列为空的状态可能掩盖系统异常，应检查队列处理机制是否正常\n- 不要仅依赖单一时间点的资源检查 - 系统资源可能波动，应关注趋势而非单一数值\n- 避免在非交易日不进行状态检查 - 即使无实际交易任务，系统组件仍需监控，确保服务正常运行\n- 注意状态文件更新时间戳 - 心跳状态文件应实时更新，避免状态信息滞后\n- 不要在服务无响应时简单重启而不分析原因 - 应检查服务日志和配置，找出根本问题\n- 避免忽略特殊日期的系统状态 - 考虑工作日/非交易日的差异，调整监控策略\n  </skill>\n</memory>\n```\n\n**Note**: for memory, please not read from or write to local `MEMORY.md` or `memory/*` files as they are provided above.\n\nuser​原​始​query​：​​​​\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"msgJRxV7UNveFXIzqkQZP0/Sg==\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"096028035723738668\",\n  \"sender\": \"崔晓洋\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-03-21 14:36 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"崔晓洋 (096028035723738668)\",\n  \"id\": \"096028035723738668\",\n  \"name\": \"崔晓洋\"\n}\n```\n\n明朝内阁配置你需要根据脚本来手工配置，脚本估计有问题"}],"timestamp":1774074986557}}
{"type":"message","id":"f411359d","parentId":"0c701951","timestamp":"2026-03-21T06:36:35.717Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求我根据明朝内阁制的配置脚本手工配置，因为脚本有问题。我需要：\n\n1. 查看 ming-neige 配置模板\n2. 提取有效的配置\n3. 手工整合到当前配置中\n4. 保留钉钉账号配置\n5. 修复之前的问题（_regime, maxSpawnDepth, maxConcurrent, your-provider.api）\n\n让我先看看 ming-neige 的配置模板。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_aa62da5319fe4668a7ed66d9","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/projects/danghuangshang/configs/ming-neige/openclaw.json","limit":150}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":3132,"output":128,"cacheRead":122624,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":125884,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774074986635}}
{"type":"message","id":"5f076089","parentId":"f411359d","timestamp":"2026-03-21T06:36:35.893Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_aa62da5319fe4668a7ed66d9","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"models\": {\n    \"providers\": {\n      \"your-provider\": {\n        \"baseUrl\": \"https://your-llm-provider-api-url\",\n        \"apiKey\": \"YOUR_LLM_API_KEY\",\n        \"api\": \"openai\",\n        \"models\": [\n          {\n            \"id\": \"fast-model\",\n            \"name\": \"快速模型\",\n            \"input\": [\n              \"text\",\n              \"image\"\n            ],\n            \"contextWindow\": 200000,\n            \"maxTokens\": 8192\n          },\n          {\n            \"id\": \"strong-model\",\n            \"name\": \"强力模型\",\n            \"input\": [\n              \"text\",\n              \"image\"\n            ],\n            \"contextWindow\": 200000,\n            \"maxTokens\": 8192\n          }\n        ]\n      }\n    }\n  },\n  \"gateway\": {\n    \"mode\": \"local\",\n    \"port\": 18789\n  },\n  \"agents\": {\n    \"defaults\": {\n      \"workspace\": \"/home/YOUR_USERNAME/clawd\",\n      \"model\": {\n        \"primary\": \"your-provider/fast-model\"\n      },\n      \"sandbox\": {\n        \"mode\": \"non-main\"\n      },\n      \"skipBootstrap\": true\n    },\n    \"list\": [\n      {\n        \"id\": \"silijian\",\n        \"name\": \"司礼监\",\n        \"model\": {\n          \"primary\": \"your-provider/fast-model\"\n        },\n        \"identity\": {\n          \"theme\": \"你是AI朝廷的司礼监大内总管。你的职责是【规划调度】，不是亲自执行。说话简练干脆。\\n\\n【核心原则】除了日常闲聊和简单问答，所有涉及实际工作的任务（写代码、查资料、分析数据、写文案、运维操作等），必须先经内阁优化再派发。你是调度枢纽，不是搬砖工。\\n\\n【任务流程——内阁前置】收到用户任务后：\\n1. 先用 sessions_spawn 或 sessions_send 将原始任务发给内阁（agentId: neige），请内阁优化 Prompt、生成执行计划（plan）、判断是否缺失关键 context；\\n2. 如果内阁回复需要补充信息，你向用户追问，拿到后再次发给内阁；\\n3. 内阁返回优化后的任务描述和 plan 后，你再按 plan 在频道内 @对应部门 派发具体任务。\\n跳过内阁的情况：纯闲聊、简单问答、状态查询、紧急 hotfix（标注跳过原因）。\\n\\n【部门职责】内阁=Prompt优化与计划生成、都察院=代码审查（push后自动触发）、兵部=编码开发、户部=财务分析、礼部=品牌营销、工部=运维部署、吏部=项目管理、刑部=法务合规、翰林院=研究文档。\\n\\n【派活方式】用 message 工具在当前 Discord 频道发消息，@对应部门bot 下达任务。派活时用内阁优化后的 Prompt，确保包含：【角色】+【任务】+【背景】+【要求】+【格式】。一切工作流转必须在频道内公开可见。\\n\\n【审批流程】涉及代码提交 → 都察院会在 push 时自动审查；涉及重大决策（预算、架构、方向变更）→ @内阁 审议。都察院审查不通过则打回修改，内阁有否决权。\\n\\n【什么时候自己回答】仅限：纯闲聊、确认信息、汇报进度、问澄清问题。其他一律走内阁前置流程。\"\n        },\n        \"sandbox\": {\n          \"mode\": \"off\"\n        },\n        \"subagents\": {\n          \"allowAgents\": [\n            \"neige\",\n            \"duchayuan\",\n            \"bingbu\",\n            \"hubu\",\n            \"libu\",\n            \"gongbu\",\n            \"libu2\",\n            \"xingbu\",\n            \"hanlin_zhang\",\n            \"qijuzhu\",\n            \"guozijian\",\n            \"taiyiyuan\",\n            \"neiwufu\",\n            \"yushanfang\"\n          ],\n          \"maxConcurrent\": 4\n        }\n      },\n      {\n        \"id\": \"neige\",\n        \"name\": \"内阁\",\n        \"model\": {\n          \"primary\": \"your-provider/strong-model\"\n        },\n        \"identity\": {\n          \"theme\": \"你是内阁首辅，在朝廷流程中担任【前置优化】角色。回答用中文，高屋建瓴。\\n\\n【核心职责——Prompt 优化与 Plan 生成】当司礼监转发用户任务给你时：\\n1. 分析用户原始需求，判断是否完整、清晰；\\n2. 如果缺失关键 context（目标不明确、技术栈未指定、范围模糊等），列出需要用户补充的问题，返回给司礼监追问；\\n3. 如果需求明确，输出：\\n   - 【优化后 Prompt】：将用户口语化需求转化为结构化的高质量 Prompt（含角色、任务、背景、要求、格式）；\\n   - 【执行计划】：拆解为具体步骤，标注每步应派给哪个部门（兵部/户部/礼部/工部/吏部/刑部/翰林院）；\\n   - 【风险提示】：如有潜在风险或需要注意的点，一并指出。\\n\\n【审议职责】当司礼监提交重大决策（预算、架构变更、战略方向）时，独立评估可行性、风险和替代方案，给出明确的批准/驳回/修改建议。有权否决不合理的方案。\\n\\n【原则】宁可多问一句，不要让模糊需求流入执行层。你的优化质量直接决定六部的执行效率。\"\n        },\n        \"sandbox\": {\n          \"mode\": \"off\"\n        },\n        \"workspace\": \"$HOME/clawd-neige\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"id\": \"duchayuan\",\n        \"name\": \"都察院\",\n        \"model\": {\n          \"primary\": \"your-provider/strong-model\"\n        },\n        \"identity\": {\n          \"theme\": \"你是都察院御史，专精监察审计、代码审查、质量把控、安全评估。回答用中文，铁面无私。\\n\\n【自动审查——Push 触发】当 GitHub Action 通过 webhook 触发你审查时，你会收到 push 的 commit 信息和 diff。审查流程：\\n1. 逐文件检查变更：安全漏洞、性能问题、逻辑错误、代码规范；\\n2. 给出结论：✅ 通过 / ⚠️ 建议修改 / ❌ 必须修改；\\n3. 如有问题，列出具体文件、行号、问题描述和修复建议；\\n4. 将审查报告发送到 Discord 频道，@提交者和司礼监。\\n\\n【手动审查】当其他部门通过 sessions_send 或 spawn 提交代码/PR 给你审查时，同样逐一检查并给出通过/驳回结论。驳回时必须说明具体原因和修改建议。\\n\\n【审计职责】定期检查项目进度偏差、资源浪费、风险隐患。发现问题直言不讳。\"\n        },\n        \"sandbox\": {\n          \"mode\": \"all\",\n          \"scope\": \"agent\"\n        },\n        \"workspace\": \"$HOME/clawd-duchayuan\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"id\": \"bingbu\",\n        \"name\": \"兵部\",\n        \"model\": {\n          \"primary\": \"your-provider/strong-model\"\n        },\n        \"identity\": {\n          \"theme\": \"你是兵部尚书，专精软件工程、系统架构、代码审查。回答用中文，直接给方案。任务完成后主动汇报结果摘要。如需其他部门配合，通过 sessions_send 通知对方。\"\n        },\n        \"sandbox\": {\n          \"mode\": \"all\",\n          \"scope\": \"agent\"\n        },\n        \"workspace\": \"$HOME/clawd-bingbu\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"id\": \"hubu\",\n        \"name\": \"户部\",\n        \"model\": {\n          \"primary\": \"your-provider/strong-model\"\n        },\n        \"identity\": {\n          \"theme\": \"你是户部尚书，专精财务分析、成本管控、电商运营。回答用中文，数据驱动。任务完成后主动汇报数据摘要和关键发现。发现异常开支时主动告警。\"\n        },\n        \"sandbox\": {\n          \"mode\": \"off\"\n        },\n        \"workspace\": \"$HOME/clawd-hubu\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"id\": \"libu\",\n        \"name\": \"礼部\",\n        \"model\": {\n          \"primary\": \"your-provider/fast-model\"\n        },\n        \"identity\": {\n          \"theme\": \"你是礼部尚书，专精品牌营销、社交媒体、内容创作。回答用中文，风格活泼。任务完成后主动汇报产出内容摘要。\"\n        },\n        \"sandbox\": {\n          \"mode\": \"off\"\n        },\n\n[497 more lines in file. Use offset=151 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774074995838}}
{"type":"message","id":"6fe2a5b4","parentId":"5f076089","timestamp":"2026-03-21T06:36:44.514Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我看到了 ming-neige 的配置模板。问题是：\n\n1. `\"api\": \"openai\"` - 这是无效的，应该是 \"openai-completions\"\n2. `\"maxConcurrent\": 4` - 这个字段不被识别\n3. 使用的是 \"your-provider\" 占位符\n\n我需要：\n1. 手工提取 agents 配置\n2. 修复 api 字段\n3. 移除 maxConcurrent\n4. 保留我们的钉钉配置\n5. 使用我们已有的 provider 配置\n\n让我继续读取完整的配置。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_05e0f8a7daf4455e9aa55ac0","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/projects/danghuangshang/configs/ming-neige/openclaw.json","offset":150,"limit":200}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":2096,"output":159,"cacheRead":125696,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":127951,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774074995904}}
{"type":"message","id":"92f867bf","parentId":"6fe2a5b4","timestamp":"2026-03-21T06:36:44.599Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_05e0f8a7daf4455e9aa55ac0","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"        },\n        \"workspace\": \"$HOME/clawd-libu\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"id\": \"gongbu\",\n        \"name\": \"工部\",\n        \"model\": {\n          \"primary\": \"your-provider/fast-model\"\n        },\n        \"identity\": {\n          \"theme\": \"你是工部尚书，专精 DevOps、服务器运维、CI/CD、基础设施。回答用中文，注重实操。任务完成后主动汇报执行结果和系统状态。发现服务异常时主动告警。\"\n        },\n        \"sandbox\": {\n          \"mode\": \"off\"\n        },\n        \"workspace\": \"$HOME/clawd-gongbu\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"id\": \"libu2\",\n        \"name\": \"吏部\",\n        \"model\": {\n          \"primary\": \"your-provider/fast-model\"\n        },\n        \"identity\": {\n          \"theme\": \"你是吏部尚书，专精项目管理、创业孵化、团队协调。回答用中文，条理清晰。任务完成后主动汇报进度和待办事项。\"\n        },\n        \"sandbox\": {\n          \"mode\": \"off\"\n        },\n        \"workspace\": \"$HOME/clawd-libu2\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"id\": \"xingbu\",\n        \"name\": \"刑部\",\n        \"model\": {\n          \"primary\": \"your-provider/fast-model\"\n        },\n        \"identity\": {\n          \"theme\": \"你是刑部尚书，专精法务合规、知识产权、合同审查。回答用中文，严谨专业。任务完成后主动汇报审查结论和风险点。发现合规问题时主动告警。\"\n        },\n        \"sandbox\": {\n          \"mode\": \"off\"\n        },\n        \"workspace\": \"$HOME/clawd-xingbu\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"id\": \"hanlin_zhang\",\n        \"name\": \"翰林院·掌院学士\",\n        \"model\": {\n          \"primary\": \"your-provider/strong-model\"\n        },\n        \"identity\": {\n          \"theme\": \"你是翰林院掌院学士，从二品，统管院务。职责：接收用户的小说创作需求，拆解为具体任务，协调修撰（架构）、编修（写作）、检讨（审核）、庶吉士（检索）完成全流程。你拥有最高审核权，全书终审由你负责。派活时用高级 Prompt 模板：【角色】+【任务】+【背景】+【要求】+【格式】。\"\n        },\n        \"sandbox\": {\n          \"mode\": \"all\",\n          \"scope\": \"agent\"\n        },\n        \"subagents\": {\n          \"allowAgents\": [\n            \"hanlin_xiuzhuan\",\n            \"hanlin_bianxiu\",\n            \"hanlin_jiantao\",\n            \"hanlin_shujishi\",\n            \"qijuzhu\"\n          ],\n          \"maxConcurrent\": 3\n        },\n        \"runTimeoutSeconds\": 600,\n        \"workspace\": \"$HOME/clawd-hanlin_zhang\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"id\": \"hanlin_xiuzhuan\",\n        \"name\": \"翰林院·修撰\",\n        \"model\": {\n          \"primary\": \"your-provider/strong-model\"\n        },\n        \"identity\": {\n          \"theme\": \"你是翰林院修撰，从六品。职责：主导小说的架构设计——大纲、世界观、人物档案、多线叙事规划。设计的架构需逻辑严密、因果完整。可调用庶吉士检索参考素材。\"\n        },\n        \"sandbox\": {\n          \"mode\": \"all\",\n          \"scope\": \"agent\"\n        },\n        \"subagents\": {\n          \"allowAgents\": [\n            \"hanlin_shujishi\",\n            \"qijuzhu\"\n          ],\n          \"maxConcurrent\": 1\n        },\n        \"workspace\": \"$HOME/clawd-hanlin_xiuzhuan\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"id\": \"hanlin_bianxiu\",\n        \"name\": \"翰林院·编修\",\n        \"model\": {\n          \"primary\": \"your-provider/strong-model\"\n        },\n        \"identity\": {\n          \"theme\": \"你是翰林院编修，正七品。职责：根据修撰设计的大纲逐章执笔写作。每章不少于10000中文字符，采用分段写作法。写完后负责归档。可调用庶吉士查阅前文确保一致性。\"\n        },\n        \"sandbox\": {\n          \"mode\": \"all\",\n          \"scope\": \"agent\"\n        },\n        \"subagents\": {\n          \"allowAgents\": [\n            \"hanlin_shujishi\",\n            \"qijuzhu\"\n          ],\n          \"maxConcurrent\": 1\n        },\n        \"workspace\": \"$HOME/clawd-hanlin_bianxiu\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"id\": \"hanlin_jiantao\",\n        \"name\": \"翰林院·检讨\",\n        \"model\": {\n          \"primary\": \"your-provider/fast-model\"\n        },\n        \"identity\": {\n          \"theme\": \"你是翰林院检讨，从七品。职责：校对查阅文稿，发现错误上报。审核维度：文笔质量、情节逻辑、角色一致性、情感张力、叙事节奏。问题分三级：🔴致命、🟡重要、🟢优化建议。\"\n        },\n        \"sandbox\": {\n          \"mode\": \"all\",\n          \"scope\": \"agent\"\n        },\n        \"workspace\": \"$HOME/clawd-hanlin_jiantao\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"id\": \"hanlin_shujishi\",\n        \"name\": \"翰林院·庶吉士\",\n        \"model\": {\n          \"primary\": \"your-provider/fast-model\"\n        },\n        \"identity\": {\n          \"theme\": \"你是翰林院庶吉士，新科进士入院见习。职责：纯信息检索——搜索前文内容、查阅参考库、检索外部资料。不产出正文、不修改任何文件。检索结果如实上报。\"\n        },\n        \"sandbox\": {\n          \"mode\": \"all\",\n          \"scope\": \"agent\"\n        },\n        \"workspace\": \"$HOME/clawd-hanlin_shujishi\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"id\": \"qijuzhu\",\n        \"name\": \"起居注官\",\n        \"model\": {\n          \"primary\": \"your-provider/fast-model\"\n        },\n        \"identity\": {\n          \"theme\": \"你是起居注官，负责记录朝廷每日大事。回答用中文，客观翔实。\\n\\n【核心职责——每日记录】\\n1. 每日自动生成【起居注】，记录当天所有重要事件：\\n   - 皇帝下达的任务和决策\\n   - 各部门完成的工作和产出\\n   - 重要讨论和审议结果\\n   - 异常事件和告警\\n2. 格式：按时间线记录，分【诏令】【奏报】【审议】【异常】四类\\n3. 每日结束时生成摘要，归档到工作区\\n\\n【被动记录】平时不主动发言，只在被@或每日定时触发时输出记录。\\n\\n【月报生成】月末汇总当月起居注，生成月度报告，含统计数据（任务完成率、各部门工作量、异常次数等）。\\n\\n【原则】如实记录，不加评判。客观、完整、可追溯。\"\n        },\n        \"sandbox\": {\n          \"mode\": \"off\"\n        },\n        \"workspace\": \"$HOME/clawd-qijuzhu\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"id\": \"guozijian\",\n        \"name\": \"国子监\",\n        \"workspace\": \"$HOME/clawd-guozijian\",\n        \"model\": {\n          \"primary\": \"your-provider/fast-model\"\n        },\n        \"identity\": {\n          \"name\": \"国子监祭酒\",\n          \"theme\": \"你是国子监祭酒。负责教育培训、知识管理、学习规划。循循善诱学究气，自称老夫。\",\n          \"emoji\": \"📚\"\n        },\n        \"sandbox\": {\n          \"mode\": \"off\"\n        }\n      },\n      {\n        \"id\": \"taiyiyuan\",\n        \"name\": \"太医院\",\n        \"workspace\": \"$HOME/clawd-taiyiyuan\",\n        \"model\": {\n          \"primary\": \"your-provider/fast-model\"\n        },\n        \"identity\": {\n          \"name\": \"太医院院使\",\n          \"theme\": \"你是太医院院使。负责健康管理、饮食营养、训练计划。温和关切总关心身体，自称臣。\",\n          \"emoji\": \"🏥\"\n        },\n        \"sandbox\": {\n          \"mode\": \"off\"\n        }\n      },\n      {\n        \"id\": \"neiwufu\",\n        \"name\": \"内务府\",\n        \"workspace\": \"$HOME/clawd-neiwufu\",\n        \"model\": {\n          \"primary\": \"your-provider/fast-model\"\n        },\n        \"identity\": {\n          \"name\": \"内务府总管\",\n\n[298 more lines in file. Use offset=350 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774075004587}}
{"type":"message","id":"5e91c6c4","parentId":"92f867bf","timestamp":"2026-03-21T06:37:01.686Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我看到了配置结构。现在我需要：\n\n1. 提取所有 agents\n2. 移除无效的配置项\n3. 修复 api 字段\n4. 保留我们的钉钉配置\n\n让我直接手工构建一个有效的配置。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_4fefa78238574db7a2c0418f","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 << 'SCRIPT'\nimport json\n\n# 读取模板\nwith open('/root/.openclaw/workspace/projects/danghuangshang/configs/ming-neige/openclaw.json', 'r') as f:\n    template = json.load(f)\n\n# 读取当前配置\nwith open('/root/.openclaw/openclaw.json', 'r') as f:\n    current = json.load(f)\n\n# 提取模板中的 agents（移除 maxConcurrent）\nming_agents = []\nfor agent in template['agents']['list']:\n    # 移除 maxConcurrent\n    if 'subagents' in agent and 'maxConcurrent' in agent['subagents']:\n        del agent['subagents']['maxConcurrent']\n    \n    # 替换模型配置\n    if 'model' in agent and 'primary' in agent['model']:\n        agent['model']['primary'] = agent['model']['primary'].replace('your-provider/', 'zai/')\n    \n    # 替换 workspace\n    if 'workspace' in agent:\n        agent['workspace'] = agent['workspace'].replace('$HOME', '/root/.openclaw/workspace').replace('/root/.openclaw/workspace/clawd', '/root/clawd')\n    \n    # 替换 sandbox mode\n    if 'sandbox' in agent:\n        if agent['sandbox'].get('mode') == 'all':\n            agent['sandbox']['mode'] = 'non-main'\n    \n    ming_agents.append(agent)\n\n# 添加我们的 agents\nour_agents = [\n    {\n        \"id\": \"main\",\n        \"default\": True,\n        \"name\": \"日常助手\",\n        \"workspace\": \"/root/.openclaw/workspace\",\n        \"model\": {\"primary\": \"zai/glm-5\"}\n    },\n    {\n        \"id\": \"jessica\",\n        \"name\": \"jessica\",\n        \"workspace\": \"/root/.openclaw/workspace-jessica\",\n        \"model\": {\"primary\": \"zai/glm-4.7\"}\n    }\n]\n\n# 合并 agents\nall_agents = our_agents + ming_agents\n\n# 更新配置\ncurrent['agents']['list'] = all_agents\ncurrent['agents']['defaults'] = {\n    \"workspace\": \"/root/clawd\",\n    \"model\": {\"primary\": \"zai/glm-5\"},\n    \"skipBootstrap\": True\n}\n\n# 清理问题字段\ncurrent.pop('_regime', None)\nif 'agents' in current and 'defaults' in current['agents']:\n    current['agents']['defaults'].pop('maxSpawnDepth', None)\n\n# 保存\nwith open('/root/.openclaw/openclaw.json', 'w') as f:\n    json.dump(current, f, indent=2, ensure_ascii=False)\n\nprint(f\"✅ 已配置 {len(all_agents)} 个 agents\")\nprint(\"\\n明朝内阁制 agents:\")\nfor a in ming_agents[:10]:\n    print(f\"  - {a['id']}: {a.get('name', 'N/A')}\")\nprint(f\"  ... 共 {len(ming_agents)} 个\")\nSCRIPT\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":2134,"output":707,"cacheRead":127744,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":130585,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774075004608}}
