{"type":"message","id":"46ca5f4b","parentId":"46c31980","timestamp":"2026-03-21T06:43:55.639Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"问题找到了！司礼监的模型配置是 'zai/fast-model'，但实际可用的模型是 'zai/glm-5'、'zai/glm-4.7' 等。模板中的 'fast-model' 和 'strong-model' 是占位符，需要替换成实际的模型名称。\n\n我需要把所有 agent 的模型配置从 'your-provider/fast-model' 和 'your-provider/strong-model' 替换成实际的模型。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_d69d5377b4584ce8a3433319","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 << 'EOF'\nimport json\n\nwith open('/root/.openclaw/openclaw.json', 'r') as f:\n    config = json.load(f)\n\n# 统计问题\nissues = []\nfor agent in config['agents']['list']:\n    model = agent.get('model', {}).get('primary', '')\n    if 'fast-model' in model or 'strong-model' in model:\n        issues.append(f\"{agent['id']}: {model}\")\n\nprint(f\"=== 需要修复的模型配置 ({len(issues)} 个) ===\")\nfor issue in issues:\n    print(f\"  {issue}\")\n\n# 修复模型配置\nfor agent in config['agents']['list']:\n    if 'model' in agent and 'primary' in agent['model']:\n        model = agent['model']['primary']\n        # 替换 fast-model -> glm-5\n        if 'fast-model' in model:\n            agent['model']['primary'] = model.replace('fast-model', 'glm-5')\n            print(f\"✅ {agent['id']}: {model} → {agent['model']['primary']}\")\n        # 替换 strong-model -> glm-4.7\n        elif 'strong-model' in model:\n            agent['model']['primary'] = model.replace('strong-model', 'glm-4.7')\n            print(f\"✅ {agent['id']}: {model} → {agent['model']['primary']}\")\n\n# 保存\nwith open('/root/.openclaw/openclaw.json', 'w') as f:\n    json.dump(config, f, indent=2, ensure_ascii=False)\n\nprint(f\"\\n✅ 已修复 {len(issues)} 个模型配置\")\nEOF\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":761,"output":465,"cacheRead":136064,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":137290,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","tim