{"type":"message","id":"c2bbdd56","parentId":"29011762","timestamp":"2026-03-21T07:25:13.897Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在需要创建一个 Docker 容器启动时自动运行的脚本。但首先需要了解用户使用的是什么容器系统（Docker/Podman），以及容器的启动方式。\n\n让我创建一个 cron 定时任务，定期检查并恢复服务，这是最简单的持久化方案。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_180bdf8e645e401fa52ec68d","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# OpenClaw 服务自动恢复配置\n# 每分钟检查一次 PM2 服务，如果 Dashboard 不可访问则自动恢复\n\n* * * * * root /root/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/ensure-pm2.sh >> /root/.openclaw/workspace/logs/cron-pm2.log 2>&1\n","path":"/etc/cron.d/openclaw-pm2-autorestart"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_77377c3fba02437b8392bb7d","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"chmod 644 /etc/cron.d/openclaw-pm2-autorestart && echo \"✅ Cron 任务已配置\" && crontab -l 2>/dev/null | grep -E \"pm2|18795\" || echo \"Cron 任务列表：\""}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_d09ad549f997450793487367","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 验证配置 ===\" && ls -lh /etc/cron.d/openclaw-pm2-autorestart && cat /etc/cron.d/openclaw-pm2-autorestart"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":287,"output":271,"cacheRead":161984,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":162542,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774077900444}}
