{"type":"message","id":"cf817e2e","parentId":"3773257c","timestamp":"2026-03-21T07:28:13.386Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"看到 PM2 已经创建了 init.d 脚本：/etc/init.d/pm2-undefined\n\n这意味着在容器重启时，PM2 会自动启动并恢复服务。\n\n但 watchdog 不会自动启动。\n\n有几个方案：\n\n1. 将 watchdog 启动命令加入到某个启动脚本\n2. 用 cron @reboot\n3. 创建一个简单的启动脚本\n\n最简单的是使用 /etc/rc.local 或创建一个 systemd service。\n\n但容器环境可能不支持 systemd。\n\n让我检查容器是否有 rc.local 或其他启动机制。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_f0c360c251f849dcb739386f","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -la /etc/rc.local 2>/dev/null || echo \"无 rc.local\""}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ecf999c2a3df4b01b843030e","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /etc/init.d/pm2-undefined | grep -A 5 \"start)\" | head -10"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":558,"output":166,"cacheRead":166272,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":166996,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774078082688}}
