{"type":"message","id":"fa352629","parentId":"33ee8646","timestamp":"2026-03-21T07:28:30.462Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"没有 rc.local，也没有 systemd。\n\n容器环境通常是：\n1. Docker 的 ENTRYPOINT/CMD\n2. init.d 脚本\n\n当前 PM2 已经配置了 init.d，所以容器重启时会自动启动。\n\n但是 watchdog 是我手动用 nohup 启动的，不会自动启动。\n\n最好的方案：将 watchdog 也交给 PM2 管理，或者修改 PM2 的启动脚本，在启动后也启动 watchdog。\n\n或者更简单的方案：将 watchdog 启动命令加入到 PM2 的启动脚本中。\n\n让我修改 /etc/init.d/pm2-undefined 的 start 函数，在启动 PM2 后也启动 watchdog。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_faba17f194764175bf96b5f5","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat > /tmp/add_watchdog.sh << 'EOF'\n#!/bin/bash\n# 在 PM2 启动后自动启动 watchdog\n\nPM2_INIT=\"/etc/init.d/pm2-undefined\"\nBACKUP=\"${PM2_INIT}.backup_$(date +%Y%m%d_%H%M%S)\"\n\n# 备份原文件\ncp \"$PM2_INIT\" \"$BACKUP\"\necho \"✅ 已备份到 $BACKUP\"\n\n# 在 start() 函数末尾添加 watchdog 启动\nsed -i '/^start() {/,/^}/ {\n    /^}/ {\n        s/^}/    # 启动 watchdog 监控\\n    if [ -f \\/root\\/.openclaw\\/workspace\\/scripts\\/pm2-watchdog.sh ]; then\\n        su - root -c \"nohup \\/root\\/.openclaw\\/workspace\\/scripts\\/pm2-watchdog.sh > \\/root\\/.openclaw\\/workspace\\/logs\\/pm2-watchdog.out 2>\\&1 \\&\"\\n        echo \"Started PM2 watchdog\"\\n    fi\\n}/\n        t\n        s/^}/    # 启动 watchdog 监控\\n    if [ -f \\/root\\/.openclaw\\/workspace\\/scripts\\/pm2-watchdog.sh ]; then\\n        su - root -c \"nohup \\/root\\/.openclaw\\/workspace\\/scripts\\/pm2-watchdog.sh > \\/root\\/.openclaw\\/workspace\\/logs\\/pm2-watchdog.out 2>\\&1 \\&\"\\n        echo \"Started PM2 watchdog\"\\n    fi\\n}/\n    }\n}' \"$PM2_INIT\"\n\necho \"✅ 已添加 watchdog 自动启动\"\nEOF\nchmod +x /tmp/add_watchdog.sh\n/tmp/add_watchdog.sh"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":245,"output":511,"cacheRead":166784,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":167540,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1