{"type":"message","id":"5fe40757","parentId":"0959be33","timestamp":"2026-03-21T07:43:32.960Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户遇到配置错误：\n```\n- agents.list.2.subagents: Unrecognized key: \"enabled\"\n```\n\n问题是 `subagents.enabled` 字段不被 OpenClaw 识别。我之前尝试添加这个字段，但这是错误的。\n\n需要：\n1. 移除所有 agent 的 `subagents.enabled` 字段\n2. 运行 `openclaw doctor --fix` 修复配置\n3. 重启 Gateway\n\n让我快速修复。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 🔧 **正在修复配置错误...**"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_5b78231f57d7487d8ac5d311","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 << 'EOF'\nimport json\n\nwith open('/root/.openclaw/openclaw.json', 'r') as f:\n    config = json.load(f)\n\n# 移除所有 agent 的 subagents.enabled\ncount = 0\nfor agent in config['agents']['list']:\n    if 'subagents' in agent and 'enabled' in agent['subagents']:\n        del agent['subagents']['enabled']\n        count += 1\n        print(f\"✅ 移除 {agent['id']} 的 subagents.enabled\")\n\n# 保存\nwith open('/root/.openclaw/openclaw.json', 'w') as f:\n    json.dump(config, f, indent=2, ensure_ascii=False)\n\nprint(f\"\\n✅ 共移除 {count} 个无效字段\")\nEOF\n"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_6c29760936cb4646a52a11ec","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw doctor --fix 2>&1 | grep -E \"Config|error|invalid|✓|✗\" | head -10"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_809a4911e1be425a8cfe381e","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ps aux | grep openclaw-gateway | grep -v grep | awk '{print $2}' | xargs -r kill -9 && sleep 2 && cd /root/.openclaw && nohup openclaw gateway > /root/.openclaw/workspace/logs/gateway.log 2>&1 & sleep 3 && curl -s http://localhost:18789/health && echo \"✅ Gateway 已重启\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":2227,"output":424,"cacheRead":174208,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":176859,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774078997307}}
