s":757,"aggregated":"✅ clawhub 命令测试：\nerror: unknown option '--version'\n\nUsage: clawdhub [options] [command]\n\nClawdHub CLI v0.3.0 (b6687e5a)\ninstall, update, search, and publish agent skills.\n\nOptions:\n  -V, --cli-version            Show CLI version\n  --workdir <dir>              Working directory (default: cwd)\n  --dir <dir>                  Skills directory (relative to workdir, default:\n                               skills)\n  --site <url>                 Site base URL (for browser login)\n  --registry <url>             Registry API base URL\n  --no-input                   Disable prompts\n  -h, --help                   display help for command\n\nCommands:\n  login [options]              Log in (opens browser or stores token)\n  logout                       Remove stored token\n  whoami                       Validate token\n  auth                         Authentication commands\n  search [options] <query...>  Vector search skills\n  install [options] <slug>     Install into <dir>/<slug>\n  update [options] [slug]      Update installed skills\n  list                         List installed skills (from lockfile)\n  explore [options]            Browse latest updated skills from the registry\n  publish [options] <path>     Publish skill from folder\n  delete [options] <slug>      Soft-delete a skill (owner/admin only)\n  undelete [options] <slug>    Restore a soft-deleted skill (owner/admin only)\n  star [options] <slug>        Add a skill to your highlights\n  unstar [options] <slug>      Remove a skill from your highlights\n  sync [options]               Scan local skills and publish new/updated ones\n\nEnv:\n  CLAWDHUB_SITE\n  CLAWDHUB_REGISTRY\n  CLAWDHUB_WORKDIR\n\n(Command exited with code 1)","cwd":"/root/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774080039333}}
{"type":"message","id":"1321ebe8","parentId":"5914d650","timestamp":"2026-03-21T08:00:54.098Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"很好！`clawhub` 命令现在可以工作了。让我测试一下其他命令","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_0877d0701eb849e3be9741e6","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 验证 clawhub 命令 ===\" && which clawhub && ls -lh /usr/local/bin/clawhub && clawhub -V"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_38c16d8efc754c1196b75599","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat >> /root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-03-21.md << 'EOF'\n\n---\n\n## ClawdHub CLI 配置\n\n**时间：** 15:59\n\n### 问题\n`clawdhub` 命令缺少 `undici` 依赖，无法正常运行。\n\n### 解决方案\n1. 安装依赖：`npm install undici` (在 /usr/lib/node_modules/clawdhub)\n2. 创建包装脚本：`/usr/local/bin/clawhub`\n\n**包装脚本内容：**\n```bash\n#!/bin/bash\nexport NODE_PATH=/usr/lib/node_modules/clawdhub/node_modules\nexec /usr/bin/clawdhub \"$@\"\n```\n\n### 验证\n```bash\nwhich clawhub    # /usr/local/bin/clawhub\nclawhub --help   # 正常显示帮助\nclawhub -V       # ClawdHub CLI v0.3.0\n```\n\n### 常用命令\n```bash\nclawhub search <query>     # 搜索 skills\nclawhub install <slug>     # 安装 skill\nclawhub list               # 列出已安装 skills\nclawhub explore            # 浏览最新 skills\nclawhub publish <path>     # 发布 skill\n```\n\n### 相关链接\n- 官网：https://clawhub.com\n- GitHub：https://github.com/wanikua/clawdhub\n\n---\n\n**更新时间：** 2026-03-21 15:59\nEOF\necho \"✅ 已更新 memory/2026-03-21.md\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":672,"output":415,"cacheRead":65920,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":67007,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774080039341}}
